334
00:21:32,991 --> 00:21:34,925
1 9h06

335
00:21:35,861 --> 00:21:37,328
Il manque 5 minutes.

336
00:21:38,196 --> 00:21:41,256
Il était peut-être aux W.-C.
ou dans l'ascenseur.

337
00:21:41,433 --> 00:21:43,833
Terrence Cook
sait se montrer discret.

338
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:47,563
